name: Tonight
detailedForecast: Snow showers likely before 11pm. Mostly cloudy, with a low around 6. Wind chill values as low as -3. Northwest wind 6 to 10 mph, with gusts as high as 24 mph. Chance of precipitation is 70%. New snow accumulation of 1 to 2 inches possible.
